{"type": "article", "id": 29793, "title": "范思哲传记电影确定主演，以及，奚梦瑶为菲拉格慕拍广告｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻", "date": "2016-07-19T03:18:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 130, "name": "伦敦"}, {"id": 1008, "name": "演员"}, {"id": 2226, "name": "欧洲"}, {"id": 4696, "name": "传记"}, {"id": 5133, "name": "西班牙"}, {"id": 10060, "name": "摄政街"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 2969, "name": "Vivienne Westwood"}, {"id": 6542, "name": "范思哲"}, {"id": 13154, "name": "露华浓"}, {"id": 30334, "name": "Polo Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 30335, "name": "Siki Im"}, {"id": 30336, "name": "Antonio Banderas"}, {"id": 30338, "name": "奚梦瑶"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160719105011vfaFhDSkZUulQHEI.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/antonio-banderas-gianni-versace-biopic\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Antonio Banderas 确认主演范思哲传记电影</b></a>｜《原罪》、《吾栖之肤》等电影的主演 Antonio Banderas，西班牙人、今年 55 岁。5 月他曾推出与瑞典高街品牌 Selected 合作的联名系列服装，此前还在中央圣马丁学院进修过服装设计。Antonio Banderas 的下一部电影将扮演传奇设计师 Gianni Versace。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/polo-ralph-lauren-to-make-regent-street-debut-on-sept-10490856/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Polo Ralph Lauren 开欧洲首家旗舰店</b></a>｜9 月 15 日又有美国大品牌进驻伦敦摄政街，即 Polo Ralph Lauren。这将是品牌在欧洲的首家旗舰店，此前只在罗马有男装售卖点，最近新增了女装。而摄政街旗舰店将包括男女装及童装，面积约为 17561 平方英尺。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/revlon-sales-gain-1-3-in-early-look-at-second-quarter-10492121/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>露华浓预估二季度销售额小幅上涨</b></a>｜美容产品集团露华浓（Revlon ）近日初步透露截至 6 月 30 日二季度的财政状况，营业收入从去年同期的 6100 万美元下降至 5200 万，净销售额则增长了 1.3% 至 4.89 亿美元。7 月 29 日将发布完整财报。<br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/valentino-fall-2016-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valentino 发布金色调为主的秋冬季广告</a>：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719103433GOQsUYSVDcZRodma.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719103434WofGpCEJ9NcbKgv8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719103435YhKqlxTzmtL04EIu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607191034351fxHzyanoOA9lde0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719103435yeU0r2aX6IZ8v3Az.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607191034354j3J5czsBQlimWCd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719103435gi89Ot3AKZcNrzhw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719103436qY0HnIEZCmlu4bFv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">雅诗兰黛推出<a href=\"http://www.buro247.me/beauty/news/estee-lauder-launches-new-lip-collection.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">全新 20 色系列唇彩</a>， Kendall Jenner 代言：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607191040421YGlr2ioTy0QHUbL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607191040420P6qCM21xZjkvpYH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.337719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719104043tV4nDc5rdC7HOpNJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.364937\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p>德国设计师 Tom Wilhelm 设计的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/tom-wilhelm-rollholz-cruiser-skateboards\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Rollholz 滑板</a>，灵感来自 70 年代用木头细致加工、再加颜料或大理石花纹的滑板设计，看起来不错：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719102952ZeVlSto6EGIwdb0Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719102952S2clW3htDF7x5ZGn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719102952q1uXxdEsg5Abo4j3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">奚梦瑶、Ine Neefs 和 Valery Kaufman 等超模<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/salvatore-ferragamo-fall-2016-campaign/#jp-carousel-298009\" rel=\"nofollow\">为 Salvatore Ferragamo &nbsp;拍摄秋冬广告</a>：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719104614qSeyY3u0NsbolELp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.753117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719104614RHlAiTPWsFEkM9yB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.753117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719104527KAXFBxHRehvu2wo3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719104528spSEVF0Alt5CX8Qy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.151439\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607191045283HJOcDdoVFKZbljR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160719104528fKjA98zWMunIrRmw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.007500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\